extends user

block description
  p
    | Fetch leagues that the user belongs to in one or more games. The leagues will be scoped to the user. This will throw an error if any of the specified games do not support league sub-resources.

block code
  | &nbsp;
  | yf.user.game_leagues(
  |   game_key,

block inputs
  .row.form-group
    .col-sm-2
      label game_key
    .col-sm-4
      input#game_key.form-control(type="text", placeholder="eg. 328")
    .col-sm-6.desc
      p
        | Game key examples: 'mlb', 'nfl', 328 (2014 MLB season), 242 (2010 NFL season). For the purposes of this demo, you can enter a comma separated list of league keys for the array.

